00:00:56.932 --> 00:00:58.773
(Tablet of the Late Master Liu Wenyu)
If you want revenge, take my life.

00:00:58.813 --> 00:01:00.133
Why involve my son?

00:01:00.252 --> 00:01:02.493
Why?

00:01:03.893 --> 00:01:04.773
Have you forgotten?

00:01:05.973 --> 00:01:07.333
The nails were hammered tightly.

00:01:07.973 --> 00:01:09.413
He wouldn't have died otherwise.

00:01:09.973 --> 00:01:10.852
Shut up!

00:01:12.693 --> 00:01:14.572
Shut up, I said!

00:01:15.493 --> 00:01:17.333
Shut up, I didn't do it!

00:01:18.400 --> 00:01:19.452
Have you really forgotten?

00:01:20.893 --> 00:01:22.613
You sealed the coffin yourself.

00:01:24.012 --> 00:01:25.292
He wasn't dead yet.

00:01:33.852 --> 00:01:35.493
How did Wenyu end up like this?

00:01:38.053 --> 00:01:38.932
How could it be?

00:01:43.852 --> 00:01:44.652
He

00:01:45.053 --> 00:01:47.212
listened to his beloved mother,

00:01:48.372 --> 00:01:49.613
ignoring his life,

00:01:50.852 --> 00:01:52.092
ignoring his cries,

00:01:52.413 --> 00:01:53.333
standing outside,

00:01:55.012 --> 00:01:55.812
strike

00:01:57.852 --> 00:01:58.613
after

00:02:01.773 --> 00:02:02.613
strike,

00:02:03.613 --> 00:02:04.893
sealing the coffin with force.

00:02:06.693 --> 00:02:07.733
With your own hands,

00:02:08.573 --> 00:02:10.733
you cut off his last chance

00:02:11.412 --> 00:02:12.692
for survival.

00:02:13.053 --> 00:02:14.092
Stop talking!

00:02:15.293 --> 00:02:16.333
Stop talking!

00:02:17.212 --> 00:02:18.853
Stop talking!

00:02:28.733 --> 00:02:29.812
But it doesn't matter.

00:02:33.972 --> 00:02:35.092
Liu Wenyu

00:02:39.293 --> 00:02:41.733
was always a demon in human skin.

00:02:43.053 --> 00:02:45.613
Wenyu, I'm Xiaohua, spare me!

00:02:51.692 --> 00:02:52.212
Go away!

00:02:52.690 --> 00:02:53.573
Liu Wenyu, let her go!

00:02:53.573 --> 00:02:54.590
Who do you think you are?

00:02:55.740 --> 00:02:58.500
Huan Xi.

00:02:59.493 --> 00:03:00.652
It's Liu Wenyu.

00:03:03.300 --> 00:03:05.090
This is the result you brought
upon yourself.

00:03:06.613 --> 00:03:08.092
You deserve it.

00:03:14.212 --> 00:03:15.333
But if it weren't you

00:03:16.853 --> 00:03:18.573
who indulging and spoiling him,

00:03:19.090 --> 00:03:20.532
he wouldn't have ended up like this.

00:03:21.573 --> 00:03:22.532
It's you.

00:03:23.293 --> 00:03:24.724
Your evil killed him!

00:03:24.725 --> 00:03:25.487
(Tablet of the Late Master Liu Wenyu)

00:03:25.812 --> 00:03:26.573
It's not me!

00:03:27.333 --> 00:03:28.053
Not me!

00:03:28.412 --> 00:03:29.092
Not me!

00:03:31.173 --> 00:03:31.773
Not me!

00:03:32.613 --> 00:03:33.252
Wenyu.

00:03:33.652 --> 00:03:34.493
(Tablet of the Late Master Liu Wenyu)
Listen to me!

00:03:34.773 --> 00:03:35.733
This is his karma!

00:03:36.532 --> 00:03:37.092
Wenyu.

00:03:38.053 --> 00:03:38.972
Listen to me.

00:03:41.652 --> 00:03:42.252
Wenyu!

00:03:44.773 --> 00:03:45.573
Not me!

00:03:46.453 --> 00:03:47.173
Not me!

00:03:48.053 --> 00:03:48.773
It's you!

00:03:49.972 --> 00:03:51.412
You killed my son!

00:03:51.812 --> 00:03:53.212
You caused my son's death!

00:03:53.893 --> 00:03:55.613
It's you who killed my son!

00:03:55.613 --> 00:03:56.372
I will kill you!

00:03:56.493 --> 00:03:57.692
I will kill you!

00:03:57.853 --> 00:03:58.412
Stop!

00:04:00.132 --> 00:04:00.652
Father!

00:04:00.692 --> 00:04:01.972
Seeing you like this,

00:04:02.932 --> 00:04:05.013
there's no trace
of the Matriarch of the Liu family.

00:04:08.293 --> 00:04:10.252
She killed my son!

00:04:11.132 --> 00:04:13.293
Killed our only son!

00:04:14.013 --> 00:04:15.812
And you still defend her?

00:04:17.332 --> 00:04:18.012
You...

00:04:18.892 --> 00:04:20.413
You examined

00:04:21.132 --> 00:04:21.692
the coffin.

00:04:22.293 --> 00:04:23.413
You nailed it.

00:04:23.853 --> 00:04:25.452
Now that it's ruined,

00:04:25.630 --> 00:04:26.973
you want to shirk responsibility.

00:04:29.252 --> 00:04:30.287
The Liu family

00:04:30.812 --> 00:04:32.853
now destroyed by your hands.

00:04:33.213 --> 00:04:34.252
If I don't divorce you,

00:04:34.892 --> 00:04:36.812
I would be unworthy
before our ancestors!

00:04:40.452 --> 00:04:42.372
She killed your son!

00:04:44.173 --> 00:04:45.772
You won't avenge him

00:04:47.493 --> 00:04:49.332
and still want to divorce me?

00:04:51.973 --> 00:04:55.413
The vent hole you promised
was also nailed shut by you.

00:04:56.892 --> 00:04:59.932
I remember you helped me
with worries over the years.

00:05:01.452 --> 00:05:03.413
I tolerate your recent recklessness.

00:05:04.533 --> 00:05:06.053
I feel the pain

00:05:06.293 --> 00:05:07.733
of losing a child too.

00:05:08.493 --> 00:05:10.132
But the dead cannot return.

00:05:13.173 --> 00:05:16.293
You still have responsibilities to bear.

00:05:16.812 --> 00:05:17.452
The Liu family

00:05:18.332 --> 00:05:19.812
needs its Matriarch,

00:05:20.653 --> 00:05:21.853
not a madwoman.

00:05:22.932 --> 00:05:24.053
(At this point,)

00:05:25.132 --> 00:05:27.533
(Liu Qinghe can still tolerate
Xie Ruilan.)

00:05:32.493 --> 00:05:33.132
Look!

00:05:33.653 --> 00:05:34.932
This is your son!

00:05:35.372 --> 00:05:36.093
Your own son!

00:05:36.533 --> 00:05:37.452
He's dead!

00:05:37.692 --> 00:05:38.812
He's dead!

00:05:39.053 --> 00:05:41.653
Even now, you still think
about the Liu family's future!

00:05:42.093 --> 00:05:44.733
You heartless demon!

00:05:45.053 --> 00:05:46.012
I will kill you!

00:05:46.413 --> 00:05:48.533
I will kill you!

00:05:48.733 --> 00:05:49.332
Enough!

00:06:05.062 --> 00:06:05.987
(Tablet of the Late Master Liu Wenyu)

00:06:56.562 --> 00:06:59.462
(Zhenbai Pavilion)

00:07:06.973 --> 00:07:07.613
Mengyan.

00:07:08.572 --> 00:07:11.533
Earlier, I conspired with your mother.

00:07:12.093 --> 00:07:13.173
You don't blame me, right?

00:07:16.372 --> 00:07:17.213
I understand.

00:07:18.173 --> 00:07:19.493
As for the dowry,

00:07:19.973 --> 00:07:21.012
if Father asks,

00:07:21.372 --> 00:07:22.533
I would gladly give it.

00:07:23.372 --> 00:07:25.173
I do not care about gold or jewels.

00:07:28.812 --> 00:07:29.493
It's just that

00:07:30.653 --> 00:07:32.173
you didn't want to trust me.

00:07:36.772 --> 00:07:37.892
It's my fault.

00:07:38.413 --> 00:07:39.293
I've wronged you.

00:07:42.452 --> 00:07:43.812
I don't blame you, Father.

00:07:45.653 --> 00:07:46.332
It's just that

00:07:47.293 --> 00:07:49.372
you seem so worried today.

00:07:51.692 --> 00:07:53.093
Has something happened?

00:07:54.012 --> 00:07:56.452
Mother hasn't been well lately.

00:07:57.613 --> 00:07:58.973
If there's anything at home,

00:07:59.372 --> 00:08:00.772
that needs my help,

00:08:02.692 --> 00:08:04.213
I will surely share your burden.

00:08:06.293 --> 00:08:07.053
All you need to do

00:08:07.973 --> 00:08:09.613
is stay by my side,

00:08:11.173 --> 00:08:12.812
and that eases my worries.

00:08:12.932 --> 00:08:14.173
I don't seek status.

00:08:14.572 --> 00:08:15.132
Only

00:08:15.653 --> 00:08:17.332
to stay by your side, Father.

00:08:18.173 --> 00:08:18.853
It's just that

00:08:20.493 --> 00:08:21.853
my body...

00:08:25.853 --> 00:08:28.892
Tomorrow I'll take you to see
a doctor for proper care.

00:08:29.372 --> 00:08:30.293
It will be as you wish.

00:08:33.532 --> 00:08:34.052
Truly?

00:08:41.132 --> 00:08:41.660
Who is there?

00:08:47.500 --> 00:08:49.870
The lord is staying here temporarily
on a case, be careful.

00:08:50.650 --> 00:08:52.512
(Zhenbai Pavilion)

00:08:54.132 --> 00:08:54.652
My Lord.

00:08:56.510 --> 00:08:57.830
Sorry to disturb you, Master Liu.

00:08:58.333 --> 00:08:59.412
I was practicing archery.

00:09:00.252 --> 00:09:01.493
Sorry, I missed.

00:09:02.052 --> 00:09:04.613
Could you help me retrieve my arrow?

00:09:12.475 --> 00:09:15.437
(Zhenbai Pavilion)

00:09:19.012 --> 00:09:21.052
Just now I was discussing
with my wife here.

00:09:23.132 --> 00:09:24.330
Sorry to disturb you, My Lord.

00:09:26.573 --> 00:09:27.132
It's nothing.

00:09:29.093 --> 00:09:30.412
I just think, Master Liu

00:09:30.813 --> 00:09:32.292
and your wife are so affectionate.

00:09:32.652 --> 00:09:34.093
Your son is not yet buried,

00:09:34.412 --> 00:09:36.853
yet here you are sweet-talking
under the moonlight.

00:09:37.093 --> 00:09:38.213
So romantic.

00:09:40.652 --> 00:09:43.372
Later I still have to pray for Wenyu.

00:09:43.973 --> 00:09:45.333
I won't disturb you, My Lord.

00:09:45.813 --> 00:09:46.733
Rest early.

00:09:46.973 --> 00:09:47.933
Master Liu, please.

00:09:49.453 --> 00:09:50.012
Ruilan.

00:09:51.350 --> 00:09:52.693
You may return to your room first.

00:09:54.500 --> 00:09:58.987
(Zhenbai Pavilion)

00:10:11.462 --> 00:10:14.462
(Liu Residence)

00:10:17.333 --> 00:10:17.933
Young Madam.

00:10:18.030 --> 00:10:19.290
Master is waiting at the clinic.

00:10:26.350 --> 00:10:27.800
(Liu Residence)

00:10:32.062 --> 00:10:34.225
(Liu Residence)

00:10:35.933 --> 00:10:36.853
Liu Wenyu has awakened.

00:10:37.733 --> 00:10:39.292
Already sent away as you instructed.

00:10:40.093 --> 00:10:41.372
Don't interfere with the rest.

00:10:41.933 --> 00:10:43.372
I had him take the fake-death potion,

00:10:45.132 --> 00:10:46.252
sparing his life.

00:10:47.333 --> 00:10:49.213
He was born merely as a pawn.

00:10:51.933 --> 00:10:53.573
No one taught him right from wrong.

00:10:54.093 --> 00:10:55.453
Next is Liu Qinghe.

00:10:55.853 --> 00:10:57.613
But I don't want you to continue.

00:11:02.333 --> 00:11:03.333
As a pawn,

00:11:04.012 --> 00:11:04.853
you should know

00:11:05.412 --> 00:11:07.453
when to stop, and know when to quit.

00:11:13.292 --> 00:11:14.132
Otherwise,

00:11:15.693 --> 00:11:17.012
if you go this far,

00:11:18.333 --> 00:11:19.973
you'll become a discarded piece.

00:11:21.730 --> 00:11:23.290
Thanks, My Lord, for letting it be.

00:11:23.772 --> 00:11:25.973
Then we part here and go separate ways.

00:11:28.190 --> 00:11:28.892
Stop the carriage.

00:11:30.213 --> 00:11:31.772
Don't be too reckless.

00:11:35.213 --> 00:11:35.733
What?

00:11:37.573 --> 00:11:39.453
You want to accompany me to the clinic

00:11:40.372 --> 00:11:41.213
to see my father?

00:11:42.453 --> 00:11:43.292
Don't forget

00:11:44.693 --> 00:11:45.573
who gave you

00:11:46.733 --> 00:11:48.012
this life.

00:11:55.813 --> 00:11:56.853
I return life to you.

00:12:22.813 --> 00:12:23.652
It seems like

00:12:24.333 --> 00:12:25.573
you still think I have value.

00:12:26.333 --> 00:12:27.973
Then continue using me, this pawn

00:12:28.532 --> 00:12:31.132
to eliminate the Liu family completely.

00:12:33.532 --> 00:12:34.400
Madam, we've arrived.

00:12:52.532 --> 00:12:53.613
Take care of yourself.